quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,102,"Yottotaako e nan…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen hito Jahannama, kam…ìe hi…ìe e nder ko wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin woo…óaa kon immorde e neemaaji e dakammeeji …óin ko …ìe √±ii…ìu…ìe, neemaaji ma…ì…ìe …óin ta∆¥ataa poomaa."
  21,103,"Kulol mawngol ngol hul…ìinoytaa…ìe tuma Yiite ngen rewnetee e dow yim…ìe magge …ìen, Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen ja…ì…ìora …ìe jarnugol hara hi…ìe wi'a: "Ko ndee woni √ëalaande mo'on nde wonano…óon fodeende nden ka aduna, hi…óon weltiniree nder ton …óin neemaaji …ói hawroton e mu'un"."
  21,104,"√ëalnde Men sowoyta kammu ngun yeru sowidugol …óerol e ko ngol wonndi kon e mu'un, Men moo…ìoya tageefo ngon e mbaadi ma…ì…ìe ndi …ìe taganoo ndin e mu'un ka laawol aranol, Men fodii …óum fodoore nde lunndagol alaa e mu'un, pellet, Men laatike Siinoo…ìe ko Men fodi kon."
  21,105,"Gom…óii Men winndiino ka defte …óe Men Tillini …óum e dow Nulaa…ìe …ìen …ìaawo hari Men winndii …óum ka Allauwal Reenaangal: "Pellet, leydi ndin ronoyay ndi jeyaa…ìe Alla mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe golliroo…ìe …ìen …óoftaare Makko nden, …ìen le ko Mofte Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) …óen"."
  21,106,"Pellet, no e nder koo ko Men jippini immorde e waaju ngun …ìanngal wonannde yim…ìe rewiroo…ìe Joomi mu'un ko O Sar'inani …ìe kon, ko kam…ìe woni nafitoroo…ìe …óum."
  21,107,"Men Nuliraali ma -an Muhammadu- Nulaa…óo si wanaa Yurmeende denndaangal Tageefo ngon; sabu ko sifor…óaa kon immorde e rer…óugol fii fewnugol yim…ìe …ìen e danndugol …ìe immorde e Lepte Alla …óen."
  21,108,"Maaku -an Nulaa…óo-: "Anndu ko Wahayinaa e am immorde e Joomi am ko wonndema Rewetee…óo mon On e Goonga ko Rewetee…óo Gooto, kafidaa…óo alanaa Mo ko Kanko woni Alla, …óoworee gom…óinngol Mo, e gollirgol …óoftaare Makko nden"."
  21,109,"Si …ìee …óurnike ko addu…óaa kon, maakan …ìe -an Nulaa…óo-: "Mi anndinii on wonndema min e mo'on fiyaake on no fota …ìanngude hakkunde am e mo'on, mi wonaali anndu…óo ko honnde tuma jippintee e moo…óon ko Alla fodi kon immorde e Lepte Makko …óen."
  21,110,"Pellet, Alla no Anndi ko fin√±into immorde e konngol ngol, hiMo Anndi kadi ko suu…óo ton kon e maggol, hay e huunde suu…óanaaki Mo e …óum, aray O Yo…ìa on e dow …óum."
  21,111,"Mi anndaa, no gasa hara nennanngol on Lepte …óen ko ndarndagol on, e …óaynugol, e dakmitugol on haa dummunne happaa…óo e Ganndal Alla; fii yo on duumi e geddi mo'on e majjere moo…óon."
  21,112,"Nulaa…óo Alla on (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) maaki ko O nodday…óo Jooma: "Jooma, senndir hakkunde amen e yim…ìe amen …ìen, …ìen deppitii…ìe e geddi …óin √ëaawoore Goongaare nden, ko Joomi amen Hinnorante On men wallitorta e dow ko wowloton immorde e geddi e fennugol ngol"."